language.content: बूढ़ा आदमी क्यों हँस रहा है?
ਬੁੱਢਾ ਆਦਮੀ ਹੱਸ ਕਿਉਂ ਰਿਹਾ ਹੈ?
ସେ ଗୋଟେ ବଢ଼ିଆ ହସ କଥା ପଢ଼ିଲେ।
उसने एक मज़ेदार चुटकुला पढ़ा है।
ਉਸਨੇ ਇਕ ਮਜ਼ੇਦਾਰ ਚੁਟਕੁਲਾ ਪੜ੍ਹਿਆ ਹੈ।

ఆమె పిల్లలు మాట్లాడకుండా చక్కగా చదువుకుంటున్నారు కదా!

question.text: Watching pigeons eat _________ together makes me happy, but it is sad when they all fly away.
Seeing a game of _________ at the stadium makes me happy, but it is sad when it ends.
A rainy day makes me happy, but it is sad when _________.

options.text: the sun goes away for a very long time

answers: the sun goes away for a very long time

question.text: A clean, fresh shirt makes me happy, but it is sad when _________.

answers: it gets smelly quickly on a hot day
